videos.description: Mike McGuirl flies up court and finds Dean Wade for the big two-handed stuff in traffic.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Wade throws down a dunk in traffic

videos.description: Kamau Stokes runs the fast break and throws a nice look-away pass to Dean Wade who drops the hammer to cap the play.
videos.headline: Stokes sets up Wade for nice dunk down the lane

videos.description: Makol Mawien rises up to flush a jam after the nice pass from Xavier Sneed.
videos.headline: Sneed finds Mawien for emphatic jam

videos.description: Dean Wade finds Barry Brown Jr. on the fast break for a big one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Brown throws down one-handed dunk on the break

videos.description: Matt Coleman III throws a lofty lob pass to Jaxson Hayes for the jam.
videos.headline: Hayes rises up to dunk lob pass from Coleman
